<aside class="help-callout">
  <p>
    <strong>Need help now?</strong> Call or text the National Problem Gambling
    Helpline at <a href="tel:+18006973738">1-800-MY-RESET (1-800-697-3738)</a> —
    free and available 24/7. If you are in crisis, call or text
    <a href="tel:988">988</a>, the Suicide &amp; Crisis Lifeline. You can also
    <a href="/get-help">see all the ways to get help</a>.
  </p>
</aside>
